App:

1.) Name: Floot

2.)Concept: Timed posts

3.) Target group: College students

4.) Target platforms:
	a.)iOS
		>
	b.)Android
		>
	c.)Web
		> View Only

Clients: End users, bots


Search parameters: Location, school

Posts: 

1.) Content: 
	a.) Text
	b.)	Video
	c.) Voice

2.) Max Post time:
	a.)Client: 45 seconds
	b.)Server:
		> 24 hours + 24 hours per 100 upvotes

		
3.) Min Post time:
	a.)Client: 5-7 seconds
		> Variable
	b.)Server:
		> 24 hours
		> Downvote <=0
		
4.) Actions:
	a.)Upvote
		> Increase client post time by 2
	b.)Downvote
	
	c.)Dismiss
		>Move post to recycler
		
	d.) Comment
		>Reply to post
			>Poster may opt to initiate private conversation

Messaging:

1.)Message delete from server and client 

2.) Max messages shown: 2
	a.)Sender messages
		> Deletes on thread exit
	b.)Receiver response
		> Deletes on thread exit
		
3.) Thread has no user identifiers

Users:

1.) Users  below 20% upvote:downvote ratio restrict downvote

2.) "Shadow Mode"
	a.)Semi-ban
		>Duration: until account review
	b.)Read only
		>Can view
		>Cannot post, reply to posts, upvote, downvote
		
3.) Profile:
	a.) Access
		>Hidden by default
		>Grant individual access
	c.) Photo
	d.)	School
	e.)	Major
	f.) Name
	g.) Age
	h.) Bio
	i.) Twitter
	
Answers:

1.) Content:
	a.)Questions
	b.)Answers
	
2.) Actions:
	a.)upvote
	b.)downvote


	









